<slozena_naredba>->[L_VIT_ZAGRADA, *, <lista_deklaracija>, <lista_naredbi>, D_VIT_ZAGRADA][D_VIT_ZAGRADA] : <lista_deklaracija> -> [<slozena_naredba>->[L_VIT_ZAGRADA, <lista_deklaracija>, *, <lista_naredbi>, D_VIT_ZAGRADA][D_VIT_ZAGRADA]]
<slozena_naredba>->[L_VIT_ZAGRADA, *, <lista_deklaracija>, <lista_naredbi>, D_VIT_ZAGRADA][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA] : <lista_deklaracija> -> [<slozena_naredba>->[L_VIT_ZAGRADA, <lista_deklaracija>, *, <lista_naredbi>, D_VIT_ZAGRADA][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]]

<naredba_petlje>->[KR_FOR, L_ZAGRADA, <izraz_naredba>, *, <izraz_naredba>, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>][D_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<izraz_naredba>->[*, TOCKAZAREZ][IDN, BROJ, ZNAK, NIZ_ZNAKOVA, PLUS, OP_INC, MINUS, OP_DEC, OP_NEG, OP_TILDA, TOCKAZAREZ, L_ZAGRADA]
<izraz_naredba>->[*, <izraz>, TOCKAZAREZ][IDN, BROJ, ZNAK, NIZ_ZNAKOVA, PLUS, OP_INC, MINUS, OP_DEC, OP_NEG, OP_TILDA, TOCKAZAREZ, L_ZAGRADA]
<naredba_petlje>->[KR_FOR, L_ZAGRADA, <izraz_naredba>, *, <izraz_naredba>, <izraz>, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>][D_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<naredba_skoka>->[KR_RETURN, <izraz>, TOCKAZAREZ, *][D_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<slozena_naredba>->[L_VIT_ZAGRADA, D_VIT_ZAGRADA, *][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<slozena_naredba>->[L_VIT_ZAGRADA, <lista_naredbi>, *, D_VIT_ZAGRADA][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<slozena_naredba>->[L_VIT_ZAGRADA, <lista_deklaracija>, *, D_VIT_ZAGRADA][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<slozena_naredba>->[L_VIT_ZAGRADA, <lista_deklaracija>, *, <lista_naredbi>, D_VIT_ZAGRADA][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<izraz_naredba>->[<izraz>, TOCKAZAREZ, *][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<naredba_grananja>->[KR_IF, L_ZAGRADA, *, <izraz>, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<naredba_grananja>->[KR_IF, L_ZAGRADA, *, <izraz>, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>, KR_ELSE, <naredba>][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<naredba_petlje>->[KR_WHILE, L_ZAGRADA, *, <izraz>, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<naredba_petlje>->[KR_FOR, L_ZAGRADA, *, <izraz_naredba>, <izraz_naredba>, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<naredba_petlje>->[KR_FOR, L_ZAGRADA, *, <izraz_naredba>, <izraz_naredba>, <izraz>, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<naredba_skoka>->[KR_CONTINUE, TOCKAZAREZ, *][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<naredba_skoka>->[KR_BREAK, TOCKAZAREZ, *][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<naredba_skoka>->[KR_RETURN, TOCKAZAREZ, *][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<naredba_skoka>->[KR_RETURN, <izraz>, *, TOCKAZAREZ][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<bin_i_izraz>->[<jednakosni_izraz>, *][D_UGL_ZAGRADA]
<jednakosni_izraz>->[*, <odnosni_izraz>][D_UGL_ZAGRADA]

<jednakosni_izraz>->[*, <jednakosni_izraz>, OP_NEQ, <odnosni_izraz>][D_UGL_ZAGRADA]

<bin_i_izraz>->[*, <jednakosni_izraz>][OP_BIN_I]
<bin_i_izraz>->[*, <bin_i_izraz>, OP_BIN_I, <jednakosni_izraz>][OP_BIN_I]
<bin_xili_izraz>->[<bin_xili_izraz>, OP_BIN_XILI, *, <bin_i_izraz>][D_UGL_ZAGRADA]
<bin_xili_izraz>->[<bin_i_izraz>, *][OP_BIN_XILI]
<bin_i_izraz>->[*, <jednakosni_izraz>][OP_BIN_XILI]
<bin_i_izraz>->[*, <bin_i_izraz>, OP_BIN_I, <jednakosni_izraz>][OP_BIN_XILI]
<bin_xili_izraz>->[<bin_xili_izraz>, *, OP_BIN_XILI, <bin_i_izraz>][OP_BIN_XILI]

<bin_xili_izraz>->[<bin_xili_izraz>, *, OP_BIN_XILI, <bin_i_izraz>][OP_BIN_ILI]

<bin_i_izraz>->[*, <jednakosni_izraz>][OP_I]

<izraz_naredba>->[TOCKAZAREZ, *][IDN, BROJ, ZNAK, NIZ_ZNAKOVA, PLUS, OP_INC, MINUS, OP_DEC, OP_NEG, OP_TILDA, TOCKAZAREZ, L_ZAGRADA]
<izraz_naredba>->[<izraz>, *, TOCKAZAREZ][IDN, BROJ, ZNAK, NIZ_ZNAKOVA, PLUS, OP_INC, MINUS, OP_DEC, OP_NEG, OP_TILDA, TOCKAZAREZ, L_ZAGRADA]
<naredba_petlje>->[KR_FOR, L_ZAGRADA, <izraz_naredba>, <izraz_naredba>, *, <izraz>, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>][D_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<izraz_naredba>->[*, TOCKAZAREZ][PLUS, OP_INC, MINUS, OP_DEC, OP_NEG, OP_TILDA]

<naredba_grananja>->[KR_IF, L_ZAGRADA, <izraz>, *, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<naredba_grananja>->[KR_IF, L_ZAGRADA, <izraz>, *, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>, KR_ELSE, <naredba>][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<naredba_petlje>->[KR_WHILE, L_ZAGRADA, <izraz>, *, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<naredba_petlje>->[KR_FOR, L_ZAGRADA, <izraz_naredba>, *, <izraz_naredba>, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<naredba_petlje>->[KR_FOR, L_ZAGRADA, <izraz_naredba>, *, <izraz_naredba>, <izraz>, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<naredba_skoka>->[KR_RETURN, <izraz>, TOCKAZAREZ, *][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]
<jednakosni_izraz>->[<odnosni_izraz>, *][D_UGL_ZAGRADA]

<jednakosni_izraz>->[*, <odnosni_izraz>][OP_NEQ]

<jednakosni_izraz>->[*, <jednakosni_izraz>, OP_NEQ, <odnosni_izraz>][OP_NEQ]
<bin_i_izraz>->[<bin_i_izraz>, OP_BIN_I, *, <jednakosni_izraz>][D_UGL_ZAGRADA]

<jednakosni_izraz>->[*, <odnosni_izraz>][OP_BIN_I]

<jednakosni_izraz>->[*, <jednakosni_izraz>, OP_NEQ, <odnosni_izraz>][OP_BIN_I]
<bin_i_izraz>->[<bin_i_izraz>, *, OP_BIN_I, <jednakosni_izraz>][OP_BIN_I]
<bin_xili_izraz>->[<bin_xili_izraz>, OP_BIN_XILI, <bin_i_izraz>, *][D_UGL_ZAGRADA]

<naredba_grananja>->[KR_IF, L_ZAGRADA, <izraz>, D_ZAGRADA, *, <naredba>][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]

<naredba_petlje>->[KR_WHILE, L_ZAGRADA, <izraz>, D_ZAGRADA, *, <naredba>][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]

<naredba_petlje>->[KR_FOR, L_ZAGRADA, <izraz_naredba>, <izraz_naredba>, *, <izraz>, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]

<izraz_naredba>->[<izraz>, TOCKAZAREZ, *][PLUS, OP_INC, MINUS, OP_DEC, OP_NEG, OP_TILDA]

<naredba_petlje>->[KR_FOR, L_ZAGRADA, <izraz_naredba>, <izraz_naredba>, <izraz>, *, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>][KR_BREAK, KR_CONTINUE, KR_FOR, KR_IF, KR_RETURN, KR_WHILE, TOCKAZAREZ, L_VIT_ZAGRADA]

<slozena_naredba>->[L_VIT_ZAGRADA, <lista_deklaracija>, D_VIT_ZAGRADA, *][KR_ELSE]
<slozena_naredba>->[L_VIT_ZAGRADA, <lista_deklaracija>, <lista_naredbi>, *, D_VIT_ZAGRADA][KR_ELSE]
<naredba_grananja>->[KR_IF, L_ZAGRADA, <izraz>, *, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>][KR_ELSE]
<naredba_grananja>->[KR_IF, L_ZAGRADA, <izraz>, *, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>, KR_ELSE, <naredba>][KR_ELSE]
<naredba_petlje>->[KR_WHILE, L_ZAGRADA, <izraz>, *, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>][KR_ELSE]
<naredba_petlje>->[KR_FOR, L_ZAGRADA, <izraz_naredba>, *, <izraz_naredba>, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>][KR_ELSE]
<naredba_petlje>->[KR_FOR, L_ZAGRADA, <izraz_naredba>, *, <izraz_naredba>, <izraz>, D_ZAGRADA, <naredba>][KR_ELSE]
<naredba_skoka>->[KR_RETURN, <izraz>, TOCKAZAREZ, *][KR_ELSE]
